#

Tuna Melt

15 min
$3.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

FishDairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodQuick MealEasy Recipe

Description

A classic comfort food that's easy to prepare, combining savory tuna salad and melted cheese on toasted bread.

Ingredients

  • canned tuna: 1 (5 oz) can
  • mayonnaise: 2 tablespoons
  • celery, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • cheddar cheese, shredded: 1/2 cup
  • bread (your choice): 2 slices
  • butter: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1/4 teaspoon
